EditLabel
[Prefix]
Odcl_Tree_
[Desc]
This method starts the edit process of a tree item by displaying a TextBox on top of the tree item. This method will not start the editing process if the EditLabel property of the control is set to False.
[Arguments]
ProjectFileName
\par\tab Key
[as String or Long]


